## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|------------|
| Tag rename breaks references | Medium | Low | Use atomic rename operation in store, update all notes in single transaction |
| Performance with many tags | Low | Low | Memoize tag lists, only recalculate on note changes |
| Tag name conflicts (#Work vs #work) | Low | Medium | Normalize tags to lowercase for comparison, preserve display case |
| Bundle size increase | Low | Low | Components are small, no heavy dependencies |

